</p>
<p>
If you are planning to pay by check before the course begins, or need special attention, please e-mail '.vlc_mailto_link('Laura Franklin (lfranklin1@udayton.edu)', 'lfranklin1@udayton.edu').'
</p>
<p>
If you have any technical support questions you can direct them to '.vlc_mailto_link('VLCFF Support', 'rstewart1@udayton.edu').'.
</p>
<p>
Should you have any other questions, please feel free to e-mail me, '.vlc_mailto_link('Frank Donaldson (fedonaldson@ispd.com)', 'fedonaldson@ispd.com'). '. We are looking forward to a wonderful three days on the UD campus. Here\'s wishing you the best as you wrap up the 2017-18 school year.
</p>
<p>
Yours in Christ,<br>
Frank Donaldson
</p><br><br>';
   
