  $lang['register']['email']['register-details']['message'] = "Please save this email. This is the only notification you will receive until %s.\n\nHello %s,\n\nWelcome to the Virtual Learning Community for Faith Formation. Currently you are enrolled in the following course:\n\n%s (Course Code %s)\n\n%s\n\n%s\n\nDATE COURSE BEGINS: %s\n\nFACILITATOR: %s\n\nBOOKS NEEDED:%s\n\nACCESSING YOUR COURSE: Beginning on the Saturday before the course start date you will be able to log in at:\n\nhttps://vlcff.udayton.edu/\n\nAn email reminder will be sent.\n\nUSERNAME & PASSWORD: These are the same ones that you created in your student profile.\n\nADDITIONAL MATERIALS: In order to create a true \"virtual community\", we post each student's picture and a short bio online. This gives your classmates a better sense of who you are and helps to personalize your course. If you have not already done so, you may submit your bio and upload your picture online through the \"My Profile\" link by signing in at:\n\nhttps://vlcff.udayton.edu/\n\nA short bio (100 words or less) is best.\n\nTECHNICAL SUPPORT: If you have any technical support questions you can direct them to %s.\n\nInstitute for Pastoral Initiatives\nUniversity of Dayton\n\nUsername: %s\nE-Mail Address: %s";
    
