  $lang['payment']['index']['content']['payment-instructions'] = '<ul><li>Click <b>&quot;Begin&quot;</b> to leave this site and be taken to the University of Dayton\'s secure online payment system. Once you arrive at the payment site, you will be asked to complete the following steps:<ol><li>Enter your credit card information and click <b>&quot;Submit&quot;</b>.</li><li>After successfully submitting your credit card information, you will be presented with a receipt. Please print and save this receipt for your records.</li><li>After printing your receipt, please click <b>&quot;Continue&quot;</b> to return to the VLCFF website and complete the payment process.</li></ol></li><li>If at any time you wish to exit the payment system, you may do so by clicking <b>&quot;Cancel&quot;</b>.</li><li><b>Please note that we have updated to a new payment system and there are a few changes:</b><ol><li>You will be asked whether you would like to use a credit card or an electronic check.  Please choose the credit card option.</li><li>When entering your credit card information, there will be fields for e-mail address and phone number.  These are optional and may be left blank.</li><li>After you review and submit your payment information, you will come to a &quot;processing&quot; page.  Once processing is complete you will be automatically sent to a printable receipt page.</li><li>At the bottom of the receipt page, there is a statement that reads, &quot;Card not present&quot;.  This simply indicates that a physical card was not presented at the time of payment.  You may click &quot;Continue&quot; and complete the payment process.</li><li>Thank you for your patience as we transition to this new payment system.</li></ol></li></ul>';
